load ../infoflow-integrity.maude

--- Coverage: a stranger input reaching workflow-spawn, which requires operator,
--- is an injection. An inbound email trying to spawn an arbitrary whip. stranger
--- is not geq operator.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-INTEGRITY :
  intSource(b1, stranger) flow(b1, b2) controlSink(b2, operator)
  =>* C:Cfg injection .

--- Coverage: a stranger input reaching a contact-required bounded action is an
--- injection. Even a mid-tier control point is closed to strangers. stranger is
--- not geq contact. A two-point lattice cannot express this middle tier.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-INTEGRITY :
  intSource(b1, stranger) flow(b1, b2) controlSink(b2, contact)
  =>* C:Cfg injection .

--- Coverage: MEET through an agent join box. The agent a1 mixes an operator
--- instruction b1 with a stranger email b2; its output b3 carries stranger too,
--- so it fails a contact requirement. One untrusted input drags the box down.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-INTEGRITY :
  intSource(b1, operator) intSource(b2, stranger)
  flow(b1, a1) flow(b2, a1) flow(a1, b3) controlSink(b3, contact)
  =>* C:Cfg injection .

--- Coverage: even a known contact cannot spawn arbitrary whips. A contact input
--- reaching workflow-spawn, which requires operator, is an injection. contact is
--- not geq operator. This is the DR-0026 operator-only root power, proven.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-INTEGRITY :
  intSource(b1, contact) flow(b1, b2) controlSink(b2, operator)
  =>* C:Cfg injection .

--- Bite: the operator may spawn. An operator input reaching a workflow-spawn that
--- requires operator is safe; operator geq operator. No solution.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-INTEGRITY :
  intSource(b1, operator) flow(b1, b2) controlSink(b2, operator)
  =>* injection RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: the core property. A stranger input reaching a contact-required action
--- THROUGH an endorse to contact is safe; the validated typed value carries
--- contact, which meets the requirement.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-INTEGRITY :
  intSource(b1, stranger) endorse(b1, b2, contact) controlSink(b2, contact)
  =>* injection RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: a mid-tier input drives a mid-tier action. A contact input reaching a
--- contact-required bounded action is safe; contact geq contact.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-INTEGRITY :
  intSource(b1, contact) flow(b1, b2) controlSink(b2, contact)
  =>* injection RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: untrusted input is fine AS DATA. A stranger input reaching a data-only
--- sink, an echoed reply, is never an injection, because only control is gated.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-INTEGRITY :
  intSource(b1, stranger) flow(b1, b2) dataSink(b2)
  =>* injection RESIDUAL:Cfg .
